       *******************************************
       * The program has an in-built help manual *
       *******************************************
  
      => Compile using -std=c++11 
  
1). How to enter a meaning?
  - You can write a "multiline" meaning of as much as lines as you want.
    When you're done writing, just press Enter twice.
  

2). How to exit?
  - Just press Enter when it asks to enter a word..	[ Do NOT click on the close button of the window!!! ]

                              
					

                                      *** Type "help" for more info!! ***
